      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：下午section包含Eat lunch（2分，Me）和More work（1分，Me和Cat）。整个旅程图结构是——标题My working day，两个section，上午三项下午两项，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
